<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Too tired to write notes? Just speak.</title>
    <style>
        body {font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;}
        .container {max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
        .header {font-size: 22px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;}
        .emoji-header {font-size: 28px;}
        p {font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;}
        .button {display: inline-block; background-color: #0066ff; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin: 10px 0;}
        .footer {font-size: 14px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;}
        a {color: #0066ff; text-decoration: none;}
        a:hover {text-decoration: underline;}
        h3 {margin-top: 30px;}
        ul {padding-left: 20px;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header emoji-header">Tired of typing notes after every session?</div>

        <p>Hi <%= firstName ? firstName : "there" %>,</p>

        <p>If you ever feel drained at the end of the day — but still have notes to write — this one's for you.</p>

        <p>With <strong>Dictation</strong> on Recapp, you can <strong>simply speak out a session summary</strong>, and Recapp will turn it into a structured, formatted note (like SOAP, DAP, or whatever you prefer).</p>

        <p>No typing. No formatting. Just talk — and save time.</p>

        <hr>

        <h3>🎤 How it works:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Open the client’s page</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>“Dictate Note”</strong></li>
            <li>Speak your session summary</li>
            <li>Choose the format — Recapp generates the note instantly</li>
        </ul>

        <p>🎥 <a href="https://www.notion.so/Email-Automation-23735b2e2c7780d1ad22d828180f6361?pvs=21"><strong>See Dictation in Action →</strong></a></p>

        <p><em>(Add GIF showing the flow — ideally under 15 sec)</em></p>

        <hr>

        <h3>🔐 Is it safe to use?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. Your audio is processed securely and is <strong>never stored or shared</strong>. Dictation is designed to be a private, therapist-only tool — so you can document freely and stay compliant.</p>

        <hr>

        <p>📌 Try it today after your next session. Even one dictated note can save you 10–15 minutes.</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= loginLink ? loginLink : '#' %>" class="button">👉 Log in and Try Dictation</a>
        </p>

        <p>Want a walkthrough? <a href="https://cal.com/recapp/talk-to-the-founders"><strong>Book a free session</strong></a> — we’d be happy to show you around.</p>

        <p>Warmly,</p>

        <p><strong>Team Recapp</strong></p>

        <div class="footer">
            © 2025 Recapp. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>